[  5]   0.00-5.05   sec   517 MBytes   859 Mbits/sec    0    sender
[  5]   0.00-5.00   sec   515 MBytes   864 Mbits/sec         receiver

iperf Done.

iperf3 with - Timestamp only PTP packets:
